      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "```python\nimport random\n\ndef detect_flakiness(test_func, n_runs=10):\n    results = []\n    for _ in range(n_runs):\n        try:\n            result = test_func()\n            results.append(result)\n        except Exception as e:\n            results.append(e)\n    return len(set(results)) > 1\n\ndef test_complex_flaky():\n    import random\n    r = random.random()\n    if r < 0.33:\n        return \"success\"\n    elif r < 0.66:\n        return 200\n    else:\n        raise ValueError(\"intermittent failure\")\n\ndef test_stable_complex():\n    return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"code\": 200}\n\nassert detect_flakiness(test_complex_flaky, n_runs=30) == True\nassert detect_flakiness(test_stable_complex, n_runs=10) == False\n\nprint(\"All tests passed!\")\n```",
